        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks CD for <hi rend="italic">Journal of researches</hi>.</p>  
<p>Insect genus <hi rend="italic">Elater</hi> is an exception to the rule that all luminous organs give out a green light.</p> 
            <p>Gives some observations on climbing plants at Itajahy.</p>
            <p>His study of orchids has convinced him of the value of CD’s book.</p>
        </abstract>
